  "subject": "Add webseal.conf resource path",
  "commit_message": "Add webseal.conf resource path\n\nThe webseal.conf configuration file was tried to load from different\nresource paths, if the file is not located in them the server fails\nduring its starting process. This change validates that the\nconfiguration file exists and if not it tries to load it from\nresources path.\n\nChange-Id: I45e7beeb21c520c5029c202b2028475eee95364f\nSigned-off-by: Victor Morales <victor.morales@intel.com>\nIssue-ID: SDC-993\n",
